  "summaries": [
    "<b>Bombs</b> are explosives which can be purchased from the Demolitionist and Skeleton Merchant for <span class=\"coin\" title=\"3 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"300\"><span class=\"sc\">3</span></span> each or obtained from Pots, Chests, Slimes, killing an Undead Miner, or by powering Bomb Statues. They can be used as a mining tool or a weapon, although generally the former. When used, it is thrown a few blocks away from the player and rolls if the terrain allows it. After 3 seconds, it will explode, inflicting 100 points of damage to nearby enemies and destroying multiple blocks around it. The player can also inflict harm to themselves if not careful.",
